original_title: ベストネタシリーズ ロッチ
overview: Rocchi's Best Stuff, Full of Love for Comic Stripes! A must-see for comedy fans! Rocchi's all-time best! A total of 16 stories, including the "dressing room" performed in the final of "King of Contest 2015". A collection of Rocchi's best material selected from his masterpieces, overflowing with love for comedy!
title: ベストネタシリーズ ロッチ
